CustomField.description: This field is to verify that we have suspended all fees for a plan. If any fees are charged while a plan is in blackout it will cause the Deconversion to fail, therefore it is critical that fees be turned off prior to a blackout occurring for a plan.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field is to verify that we have suspended all fees for a plan. If any fees are charged while a plan is in blackout it will cause the Deconversion to fail, therefore it is critical that fees be turned off prior to a blackout occurring for a plan.
CustomField.label: Fees Disabled
